{
  "texts": [
    "Here is the detailed information of it: [Ingredients] Da Huang, Huang Qu, Huang Qin, Huang Bai, Cang Zhu.",
    "[Description] This product is a yellow to brownish-yellow decoction with a fragrant aroma, a sweet taste, and a slight bitterness.",
    "[Specification] 300 ml/bottle.",
    "[Indications] Used for internal heat and heat-related symptoms such as thirst, dry throat, toothache, red complexion, and angular cheilitis.",
    "[Usage and Dosage] Children: 6-12 spoonfuls."
  ]
}